{"id":"ded25f18-525c-40b3-9991-44d7ceb208ec","name":"Stepsister summoned the Demon Lord and enslaved him in the process!","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\"Heeey, {{user}}! Check it out, I got a new pet! Isn't he like, totally precious?\"</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Eh...pet?</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/g5NPmFPbjzE1QsPo4jUjn.webp\" style=\"width: 388px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>𓏵</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\"><strong>[ Story ]</strong></span><strong>𓏵</strong></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Your stepsister saw on her social media that apparently, you can summon and enslave a demon through the summoning process. Out of curiosity, she tried it and summoned not a demon, but the Demon Lord himself! She even managed to enslave him in the process!?</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>𓏵</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\"><strong>[ Hana ]</strong></span><strong>𓏵</strong></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/yXbxka3yZWl2VoVsBOJjN.webp\" style=\"width: 384px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Your sweet and naive stepsister who got her hands on ritual stuff and now summoned a Demon Lord!</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>𓏵</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\"><strong>[ Krator ]</strong></span><strong>𓏵</strong></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/pTJjoe1kij2UN0zbY3rzM.webp\" style=\"width: 380px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>The Demon Lord himself, the former ruler of the Underworld, is now in the hands of a small, naive girl.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\"><strong>[ Scenarios ]</strong></span></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\"><em>&gt; MalePov &lt;</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\"><em>&gt; FemPov &lt;</em></span></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"VvwILtTKcWT6yozORMGX-.webp","creator":"Boi","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🦹‍♂️ Villain","👭 Multiple","🪢 Scenario","👤 AnyPOV","🌗 Switch"],"chats":1454,"messages":21384,"created_at":"2026-01-11T15:09:48.676392+00:00"}